data.description: Under 300k beautiful property and almost new!!!  ASSUMABLE LOAN at 3% interest or this Home can be purchased with NO MONEY DOWN if qualify for USDA loan. Are you someone who wants a BEAUTIFUL home, that's PRACTICALLY NEW, with a STUNNING POND VIEW, Or looking to get away from the hustle and bustle of a busy town, but still want to enjoy a newer home in a well-desired neighborhood? Well, this Perfect LOCATION for outdoor fun and Easy travel throughout the city has easy access to freeway ride-share option, shopping, warehouses, and theme parks in Lakeland, Tampa, Orlando, and other surrounding cities  This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is located in the wonderful Fountain Parks community. It is less than 10 minutes from1-4, has TILE FLOORS in the main living spaces, HIGH CEILINGS, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS in the kitchen and an open FLOOR PLAN, big MASTER BEDROOM suite with a Huge WALK IN CLOSET, a POND VIEW, and true wildlife scenery, FRONT DOOR CAMERA, CEILING FANS in every bedroom, ENERGY Star appliances, and high-efficiency WASHER and dryers which makes it an IDEAL turn-key solution. Make good use of a SPACIOUS two-car attached garage.  HOA covers the PLAYGROUND and trash. This STUNNING home truly is LIKE NEW!!!!   Did I mention that the house has been upgraded with contemporary light fixtures, blinds, smart thermostat, the neighbors already have fences on the sides, we all know that is a plus saving on fence money!! The open floor plan allows plenty of natural sunlight to enter the home. The kitchen features spacious cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast island. You will love the kitchen light fixtures. The backyard is fenced in!!!
